<h1> Eldest director</h1>
<% directors_with_dob = Director.where.not({ :dob => nil})%>
<%ascending_dob = directors_with_dob.all.order({:dob => :asc})%>
<%eldest_director = ascending_dob.at(0)%>


<%eldest_director_dob = eldest_director.dob%>
<%formatted_date_string= eldest_director_dob.strftime("%B %d, %Y")%>

<p>The eldest director in our dataset right now is <a href="/directors/<%=eldest_director.id%>"><%=eldest_director.name%></a>, born on <%=formatted_date_string%>.</p>
<p>(<a href="http://strftime.net/" target="_blank">http://strftime.net/</a> is handy for putting together the formatting strings for the <code>.strftime</code> method.)</p>

